The Telegraph - Calcutta : Nation

 Dixit post

New Delhi, Jan. 4: M.K. Narayanan, special 

adviser to the Prime Minister, has been assigned the additional duties of the 

national security adviser until further orders.

 Manmohan Singh will ?consult? senior colleagues over three-four days before deciding on the successor to J.N Dixit, who died of a heart attack on Monday, sources said.




